data.title: FA981 Chauncey Billups Denver Nuggets Basketball 8x10 11x14 16x20 Photo
data.meta_description: You are bidding on an 8x10, 11x14, 12x18 or 16x20 photo. 8x10 and 11x14 photos will be shipped in a clear plastic sleeve or sheet protector and have two pressboard sheets inserted in the shipping envelope to prevent bending. 12x18 and larger photos will be rolled in a hard tube in a poly bag and shipped. They are professionally printed at a photo lab not an ink jet printer. All of our photos are printed with matte / luster finish. Each photo will have a small oval authentication sticker that is serialized to ensure first generation reproduction and not a copy. Delivery Times It can take 4-6 days for orders to hit the postal system. We print the photos as they are ordered. This ensures that you get a fresh unhandled print. If you are in a rush, we are not the seller for you. Sorry.
data.text: Will ship within 4 business days of receiving cleared payment. The seller has specified an extended handling time for this item.Accepted within 30 days if sent through eBay International ShippingMoney BackBuyer pays for return shipping
